title: ★Fully Furnished Rental In Birmingham★
posting_body: ["IF THIS PROPERTY DOESN'T FIT YOUR NEEDS, FEEL FREE TO CALL OR EMAIL ME", 'I MAY HAVE OTHER PROPERTIES TO PASS BY YOU', 'show contact info', '3 Beds', '2 Baths', '1388  Square Ft', 'Fully furnished rentals like this near downtown are extremely rare!', 'This charming red brick bungalow is located just moments from downtown, on a quiet tree-lined street with lots of natural light & prepped for an easy move in!', 'The kitchen has been updated, with stainless appliances and cozy breakfast nook.', "There's also a formal dining room and spacious living room with gas fireplace for entertaining.", "On the main level, you'll discover 2 bedrooms and a full bathroom then make your way upstairs where your large master retreat & walk-in closet awaits.", 'Additional storage & living space in the partially finished basement features an updated bathroom with walk-in shower tiled floor to ceiling as well as entertainment area with built-in bar.', 'Head outside to find a large deck - complete with built-in hot tub sheltered by a gazebo canopy; perfect for relaxing with friends.', '12-Month Lease Considered.', '24-Month Lease Preferred.', 'Call this home today and submit an application!', 'The agent does not guarantee the accuracy of the square footage, lot size, or other information concerning the conditions or features of the property provided by the seller or obtained from public records or other sources.', 'The buyer is advised to independently verify the accuracy of all information through personal inspection and with appropriate professionals.', 'Presented by: Christopher Berna']
